snippet.title: Marjorie Taylor Greene Wants to Pull Guns on Vaccines: Week In Review | The Amber Ruffin Show
snippet.description:
The Amber Ruffin Show. New Episodes Streaming Every Friday on Peacock: https://pck.tv/3pOiao8

Reserve your spot in the live studio audience for The Amber Ruffin Show at https://1iota.com/show/1210/the-amber-ruffin-show

Republican Congresswoman Marjorie Taylor Greene was back in the news this week. You may remember the last time we checked in with Majorie Taylor Greene, she was shouting at Representative Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez’s staff through the mail slot on her office door. Well, last week, a new video emerged of Taylor Greene telling a bunch of supporters at a fundraiser what they should do if a government volunteer comes to their door to promote vaccines.
